{"tid":1437510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文] [經濟戰] 罷買/最低消費攻略方向","createTime":"2019-08-09T14:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T08:15:41.000Z","uid":281419,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"87fa1463dea4ac5bfa42dca71dc1e261dafb3e9c","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:19:41.000Z","msg":"最近見到大家決定實行罷買及最低消費黎打經濟戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啱今日777出聲串鳩200萬人都係對社會無貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就唔好令佢失望啦！！！<br />\n一於做盡佢打殘香港經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我決定以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>「衣食住行」</strong></span></span>為主題，希望俾各位手足有個方向去行動<br />\n不過我本身都已經係一個低消費既人，俾既意見可能會有不足<br />\n所以希望各位巴打絲打集思廣益，一齊完善呢個行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">心態/理念</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n實行「<strong>零消費</strong>」係最強亦係最困難既手段<br />\n如果本身已經做開零消費，我係非常支持你繼續實行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果你係初次接觸既話，我會建議你實行「<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">最低消費</span></strong>」-- 只買<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必需(necessary)</span></strong>既物品<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>TL;DR 去滿足「需要 (Needs)」，而唔係「慾望 (Wants)」<br />\n每次買野之前，問下自己，我唔買呢樣野會唔會影響我既生活？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n但係香港實行最低消費其實唔簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我地好多時會不自覺咁滿足自己既慾望而去消費<br />\n（我諗好多人都試過經過飲品店就會無啦啦入去買杯野飲）<br />\n而呢個時候，你就需要「<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">罷買</strong></span>」啦！！<br />\n要買野既就去支持我地既商鋪度買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一蚊都唔俾垃圾鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">1. 衣</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n唔知大家有無聽過「<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">膠囊衣櫥 (Capsule Wardrobe)</span></strong>」?<br />\n利用指定數量既衣物，mix&amp;match出唔同既配搭<br />\n唔單止可以幫大家慳番買杉既錢，亦都可以從中搵出最適合自己既風格<br />\n但係trial&amp;error當中，你可能會買到啲唔啱自己既杉，<br />\n又或者你根本無咁多錢去買唔同既杉，<br />\n呢個時候你地可以試下同身邊既親朋好友<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">交換衣物</span></strong>（當然要洗乾淨同消毒左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n進一步減少消費，亦都減少對環境既負擔<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">2. 食</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n如果大家住係街市附近既話，恭喜你已經50%擺脫對超級市場既依賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n附近無街市但係又唔想幫襯超市，<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">HKTV MALL</span></strong>幫到你<br />\n當然亦都希望大家盡量發掘下屋企附近既<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">小店</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無時間煮飯，焗住要係外面解決三餐既，唔緊要！！！！！<br />\n我地有位好勁揪既巴打已經整左個<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>罷食app</strong></span>，android/iOS都上左架啦！！！！！<br />\n邊啲鋪頭係值得幫襯既，識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1421345/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1421345/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">3. 住</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>HKTV MALL</strong></span>（無錯又係佢）係最方便既選擇之一<br />\n怕麻煩既直接一take過買晒日用品啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係用開外國牌子既話，我相信好多人（尤其係絲打）會係外國網站買，<br />\n（其實乜撚野牌子都好，好多時入到香港就貴一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n但係好多時都要過指定金額先會有免運費<br />\n大家可以考慮下開post夾下單share下運費<br />\n（不過呢樣野就講個「信」字，風險自己衡量）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">4. 行</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n最大boss沒有之一，因為狗鐵絕對係好多人既第一交通選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但咁樣唔代表我地無野可以做！！！！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>轉搭巴士/電車</ins></span><br />\n我係東區撚，而我公司亦都係東區，所以我翻工係搭叮叮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過更多人係需要跨區翻工，如果大家唔介意早些少起身，<br />\n希望大家轉搭巴士，做唔到既就放工轉搭巴士<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>減短車程</ins></span><br />\n有時候你只要早一個站上/落車，你既車錢係可以慳番一蚊兩蚊（而且無風險）<br />\n睇落好似好少，但積少成多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時亦都可以當做運動，絕對適合大家當長期鍛練下身體<br />\n<br />\n呢篇文只係提供好基本既實行方向，所以希望大家提供下自己係日常生活既行動，<br />\n大家亦都可以參考唔同巴打絲打既方法，繼續完善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba077e2f2fcc03c259901176fd5b69642d09396d","tid":1437510,"uid":78098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:23:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65e9748f4f58422f97dd21f1466ad6eab7ea49da","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:23:33.000Z","msg":"繼續攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d85c5c7a2bf555c8c688e5b36a44dfa9685bc5","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"攬炒巴第11波行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1437238/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1437238/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2857f817e6a4d26998a19a622c6288aa13983676","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:29:07.000Z","msg":"真。對準政權系列：中國共產黨不想香港人知道的秘密<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437411\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437411</a>"},{"pid":"6234c5e0aa75338b9615713f03872111ccb9855f","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"罷買行動補充！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n[請廣傳] 支持黃商抵制藍商救港app「自由篩」已成形，短期內推出上架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423228</a>"},{"pid":"b6d8b1bf39553a1d4f742b0ba4cd63129b26d8ef","tid":1437510,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"午餐帶飯，依家啲嘢愈來愈貴又唔好食"},{"pid":"8af82078320f1af12e709c103d28f4e3935ed306","tid":1437510,"uid":300830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"我會罷買"},{"pid":"c39eac5b1f2263d8bed4abb8214a81dd8975ff8e","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6d8b1bf39553a1d4f742b0ba4cd63129b26d8ef","tid":1437510,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"午餐帶飯，依家啲嘢愈來愈貴又唔好食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:42:38.000Z","msg":"其實我都係自己帶飯<br />\n除左出面啲lunch貴<br />\n仲有<br />\n1. 唔健康<br />\n有時啲餐好肥膩但係都係焗住要食<br />\n2. 太大份<br />\n作為女仔真係食唔到咁多<br />\n但又唔想浪費結果夾硬食晒<br />\n其實對個胃唔好"},{"pid":"6be0f2089b6900d7e5a84334e540d3a6930ccfba","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af82078320f1af12e709c103d28f4e3935ed306","tid":1437510,"uid":300830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"我會罷買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d8224cfae87043fef0582added8e3a71ba6e83","tid":1437510,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41fd379cb1f01675e6935fd10def6596a5d1803","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"各位手足要撐住！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n温馨提示：美國國會，係9月9日復會，然後會討論香港人權法，港共政府想哩三十日壓平所有示威活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437458\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437458</a>"},{"pid":"f54da56b180f325716313a7b6933e33e924bbcc1","tid":1437510,"uid":39239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"仲有嚟緊要罷買月餅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044a7804309b950a385bcc1d6796c53004a3853b","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f54da56b180f325716313a7b6933e33e924bbcc1","tid":1437510,"uid":39239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"仲有嚟緊要罷買月餅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"唔講差啲唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99541d9eab8b7294495d597e5e93b4ebada72969","tid":1437510,"uid":199339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"聽日大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436835/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436835/page/1</a><br />\n入黎幫手推記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a00901066669534b4ba91d0c86084247e097f44","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99541d9eab8b7294495d597e5e93b4ebada72969","tid":1437510,"uid":199339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"聽日大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436835/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436835/page/1</a><br />\n入黎幫手推記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"已推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0bf98869890cc9c8fd789fc9a4b41dbf143988","tid":1437510,"uid":281926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">It is now or never</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12MG0mw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12MG0mw.jpg&h=36b78f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JbRLHyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJbRLHyB.jpg&h=1e584e56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0RU9pMh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0RU9pMh.jpg&h=badbf015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mArf4Mh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmArf4Mh.jpg&h=33593d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMjYh6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMjYh6i.jpg&h=cb0a758f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJe5HxY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJe5HxY.jpg&h=c0bf2354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rhb7VSZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frhb7VSZ.jpg&h=f44402b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebf342d42e15178e223a00352c9bf3bc2d87a371","tid":1437510,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"我有個建議，你可以罷買本地產品黎影響零售，但有問題係有人會為左就呢兩日，係前一日或後一日增加消費，咁樣既話其實作用不大，咁不如教香港人去海購或amazon黎訂野黎"},{"pid":"c1f4c6f2e6b79209ced05b4f9728654c3c45498c","tid":1437510,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebf342d42e15178e223a00352c9bf3bc2d87a371","tid":1437510,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"我有個建議，你可以罷買本地產品黎影響零售，但有問題係有人會為左就呢兩日，係前一日或後一日增加消費，咁樣既話其實作用不大，咁不如教香港人去海購或amazon黎訂野黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:16:06.000Z","msg":"或者 hktvmall?"},{"pid":"c8812b7d7a72886a48726c589bea23ee615b287a","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebf342d42e15178e223a00352c9bf3bc2d87a371","tid":1437510,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"我有個建議，你可以罷買本地產品黎影響零售，但有問題係有人會為左就呢兩日，係前一日或後一日增加消費，咁樣既話其實作用不大，咁不如教香港人去海購或amazon黎訂野黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:39:28.000Z","msg":"我相信指定日子罷買係主要想減低不必要既消費<br />\n反而日常生活既消費（主要係食）需要罷買大商家<br />\n從而將收益轉為俾小商店以作抗衡<br />\n<br />\n當然海外網購係更加直接影響本地零售<br />\n所以我個人會更偏向將海外網購應用係「衣」、「住」兩個方向"},{"pid":"383b708126a0a51de52374f9646bfd7244851888","tid":1437510,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c90e86aac9682c27df1592ced21ebdfdad981ab","tid":1437510,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:44:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c59b817d318b5d4fff5271e69d2e4d22ca2f328","tid":1437510,"uid":301929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ks7nLjT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKs7nLjT.jpg&h=a2b51b13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VH8VkTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVH8VkTe.jpg&h=7165608a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"befb59e0083f5607020a739b96d734cec50c8a2d","tid":1437510,"uid":300602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a155e5d0c718f22450de23bbc4d2581d04a6663e","tid":1437510,"uid":281419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"再補充<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins>5. 護膚品/化妝品</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n化妝品其實係最易賺既product<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係點解Estee Lauder、LANC&Ocirc;ME個啲會開到成行成市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然好難，但我懇請巴打絲打們儘量減少買化妝品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（工作需要除外）<br />\n認真，化妝某程度上都係傷皮膚，可免則免<br />\n（而作為半個IT狗既我係日日素顏翻工，我認我殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n至於護膚品，我係唔會強求各位巴打絲打罷買大牌子<br />\n因為有敏感性皮膚既人係唔可以亂用護膚品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你地可以罷買連鎖店，經海外網購/小店買<br />\n可以既話，希望大家可以支持一下香港同台灣既小眾品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港既係IG會間唔中見到廣告，而台灣既可以上pinkoi睇睇<br />\n至於海外既品牌，我諗絲打們應該都熟門路架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}